# JavaScript  debounce
JavaScript  debounce [](https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Closures).

```js
function debounce(fn, wait) {
  let timeout = null;
  return function() {
    if (timeout !== null) clearTimeout(timeout);
    timeout = setTimeout(fn, wait);
  };
}
